# Code owners for security and quality control
# Military-grade access control principles

# Global owners (security team)
* @security-team @maintainers

# Security-critical files
.github/ @security-team
.github/workflows/ @security-team @ci-team
.github/codeql-config.yml @security-team
.github/dependabot.yml @security-team
.github/CODEOWNERS @security-team

# API security
api/src/core/ @security-team @backend-team
api/src/middlewares/ @security-team @backend-team
api/src/services/ @security-team @backend-team

# Infrastructure security
infrastructure/ @security-team @devops-team
infrastructure/kubernetes/ @security-team @devops-team
infrastructure/terraform/ @security-team @devops-team

# Frontend security
app/ @frontend-team
app/components/ @frontend-team

# Documentation
docs/ @documentation-team
runbooks/ @documentation-team @security-team

# Tests
api/src/tests/ @qa-team @backend-team
**/*.test.* @qa-team
**/*.spec.* @qa-team

# Configuration files
*.config.* @devops-team
*.toml @backend-team
*.json @frontend-team
*.yml @devops-team
*.yaml @devops-team

# Require security review for changes to these patterns
/SECURITY.md @security-team
/package.json @security-team
/Cargo.toml @security-team
/Dockerfile* @security-team @devops-team